## Expectation Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Understand what the stakeholder expects (vs. what is realistic)
- [ ] 2. Assess the gap between expectations and reality
- [ ] 3. Prepare data-backed context to frame the conversation
- [ ] 4. Communicate the realistic picture proactively
- [ ] 5. Negotiate aligned expectations with clear commitments
- [ ] 6. Document agreements and follow up in writing
- [ ] 7. Monitor and gently reset if expectations drift again

## Key Inputs
- Stakeholder: {{stakeholder}}
- Current Expectation: {{current_expectation}}
- Reality/Constraints: {{reality_constraints}}
- Communication Context: {{communication_context}}
